Step 1
Customer selects a product.

↓

Step 2
Checkout page.

↓

Step 3
Customer selects
Prepayment.

↓

Step 4
Customer clicks
"Place Order"

↓

Step 5
Merchant sends API request to Novalnet.

↓

Step 6
Novalnet validates:
• Merchant credentials
• Required parameters
• Amount
• Currency
• Payment method

↓

Step 7
Novalnet generates a TID.

↓

Step 8
Novalnet creates a prepayment transaction.

↓

Step 9
Novalnet returns:
• TID
• Payment Instructions
• Bank Account Details
• Payment Reference
